#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:486
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:685
msgid "Detailed Parameter Descriptions"
msgstr "参数详解"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**world properties**"
msgstr "**world 属性**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:492
msgid "**`name`** (`str`, default: `\"world\"`)"
msgstr "**`name`**（`str`，默认： `\"world\"`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:493
msgid ""
"Defines the name of the world used in the simulation. This can be useful "
"for identifying different simulation environments."
msgstr "定义仿真使用的世界名称，便于区分不同环境。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:496
msgid "**`height`** (`float`, default: `10`)"
msgstr "**`height`**（`float`，默认 `10`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:497
msgid ""
"Specifies the vertical size of the world in units of meters in the Y-axis"
" direction plotted on the screen."
msgstr "指定世界在屏幕 Y 轴方向的垂直尺寸（米）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:500
msgid "**`width`** (`float`, default: `10`)"
msgstr "**`width`**（`float`，默认 `10`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:501
msgid ""
"Specifies the horizontal size of the world in units of meters in the "
"X-axis direction plotted on the screen."
msgstr "指定世界在屏幕 X 轴方向的水平尺寸（米）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:504
msgid "**`step_time`** (`float`, default: `0.1`)"
msgstr "**`step_time`**（`float`，默认 `0.1`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:505
msgid "Determines the time interval between each simulation step."
msgstr "决定仿真每一步之间的时间间隔。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:507
msgid ""
"**Performance Impact**: A smaller `step_time` results in a higher "
"simulation frequency (e.g., `0.1` seconds corresponds to 10 Hz) but needs"
" longer time to run the simulation."
msgstr "**性能影响**：`step_time` 越小仿真频率越高（如 0.1 秒即 10 Hz），但仿真耗时也更长。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:510
msgid "**`sample_time`** (`float`, default: `step_time`)"
msgstr "**`sample_time`**（`float`，默认与 `step_time` 相同）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:511
msgid ""
"Defines the time interval for rendering the simulation and extracting "
"data. This controls how frequently visual updates and data recordings "
"occur. If not specified, defaults to the value of `step_time`."
msgstr "定义渲染与数据采集的时间间隔，决定可视化更新与记录的频率。未指定时默认等于 `step_time`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:514
msgid "**`offset`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[0, 0]`)"
msgstr "**`offset`**（`float` 列表，默认 `[0, 0]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:515
msgid ""
"Sets the initial positional offset of the world on the X and Y axes. This"
" is useful for positioning the world within a larger coordinate system or"
" for relative placement."
msgstr "设置世界在 X、Y 轴上的初始偏移，便于在更大坐标系中定位或相对放置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**world mode**"
msgstr "**world 模式**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:522
msgid "**`control_mode`** (`str`, default: `\"auto\"`)"
msgstr "**`control_mode`** (`str`, 默认： `\"auto\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:523
msgid "Configures how the objects in the simulation are controlled:"
msgstr "配置仿真中对象的被控方式："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:525
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:533
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:542
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:717
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:882
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1052
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1091
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1191
msgid "**Options:**"
msgstr "**选项:**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:526
msgid ""
"`auto`: Automatic control by the input velocities defined in python "
"script or behavior in the YAML file."
msgstr "`auto`：通过 Python 脚本中定义的输入速度或 YAML 文件中的行为进行自动控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:527
msgid ""
"`keyboard`: Manual control via keyboard inputs. The key inputs are "
"defined in the file."
msgstr "`keyboard`：通过键盘输入进行手动控制。按键输入在文件中定义。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:530
msgid "**`collision_mode`** (`str`, default: `\"stop\"`)"
msgstr "**`collision_mode`** (`str`, 默认： `\"stop\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:531
msgid "Defines how collisions between objects are handled in the simulation:"
msgstr "定义仿真中对象碰撞的处理方式："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:534
msgid "`stop`: Stops the movement of objects upon collision. (default)"
msgstr "`stop`：发生碰撞时立即停止（默认）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:535
msgid ""
"`unobstructed`: Allows objects to pass through each other without "
"consideration of any collision."
msgstr "`unobstructed`：允许对象彼此穿过，不考虑任何碰撞。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:536
msgid ""
"`unobstructed_obstacles`: Only allows obstacles to pass through each "
"other without consideration of any collision. The robots will stop when "
"they are in collision with the obstacles."
msgstr "`unobstructed_obstacles`：仅允许障碍物彼此穿过而不考虑碰撞；机器人与障碍物发生碰撞时仍会停止。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:539
msgid "**`status`** (`str`, default: `\"None\"`)"
msgstr "**`status`** (`str`, 默认值： `\"None\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:540
msgid "Sets the initial status of the simulation environment:"
msgstr "设置仿真环境的初始状态："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:543
msgid "`\"Running\"`: The simulation runs normally (default)."
msgstr "`\"Running\"`：仿真正常运行（默认）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:544
msgid "`\"Pause\"`: The simulation starts in a paused state."
msgstr "`\"Pause\"`: 仿真初始状态为暂停。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:545
msgid "`\"Arrived\"`: The simulation stops when the robot arrives at the goal."
msgstr "`\"Arrived\"`: 仿真在机器人到达目标点的时候停止。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:546
msgid ""
"`\"Collision\"`: The simulation stops when the robot collides with an "
"obstacle."
msgstr "`\"Collision\"`: 仿真在机器人与障碍物发生碰撞时停止。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:548
msgid ""
"**Note**: The status can be dynamically changed during simulation using "
"keyboard controls (space key) or programmatically."
msgstr "**注意**：仿真过程中可以通过键盘（空格键）或程序控制动态切换状态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**world map**"
msgstr "**world 地图**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:555
msgid "**`obstacle_map`** (`dict`, `str`, `ndarray`, or `null`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`obstacle_map`**（`dict`、`str`、`ndarray` 或 `null`，默认值：`None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:556
msgid ""
"Occupancy grid source. **Canonical form is a generator spec dict** with "
"``name``; other types are convenience/backward compat."
msgstr "占据栅格来源。**标准形式是带 ``name`` 的生成器配置字典**；其他类型为便捷写法/向后兼容。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:558
msgid ""
"**Generator spec** (`dict`): ``name`` identifies the generator. ``name: "
"image`` with ``path`` (e.g. ``'cave.png'``) loads an image; grid size "
"from the image. ``name: perlin`` (and others) require ``resolution``; "
"grid size = world size / resolution. See [Configure grid "
"map](../usage/configure_grid_map.md). To add a new generator, see [Adding"
" a new map generator](../usage/configure_grid_map.md#adding-a-new-map-"
"generator)."
msgstr ""
"**生成器配置**（`dict`）：``name`` 标识生成器。``name: image`` 配合 ``path``（例如 "
"``'cave.png'``）从图像加载，栅格大小取自图像。``name: perlin``（及其他）需要 ``resolution``；栅格大小"
" = 世界大小 / resolution。参见 "
"[配置栅格地图](../usage/configure_grid_map.md)。要新增生成器，参见 "
"[新增地图生成器](../usage/configure_grid_map.md#adding-a-new-map-generator)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:559
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Image path** (`str`): Treated as ``{ name: image, path: obstacle_map "
"}`` (backward compat)."
msgstr "**图像路径**（`str`）：等价于 ``{ name: image, path: obstacle_map }``（向后兼容）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:560
msgid ""
"**Occupancy grid** (`ndarray`): Programmatic use only. Float 0–100; world"
" size must match grid shape."
msgstr "**占据栅格**（`ndarray`）：仅供编程方式使用。浮点值 0–100；世界大小必须与栅格形状匹配。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:561
msgid "**`null`**: No obstacle map (empty world)."
msgstr "**`null`**：无障碍物地图（空世界）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:563
msgid ""
"**Available Maps**: We provide some example maps in the `irsim/world/map`"
" folder and you can also use your own map by 3D datasets like "
"[HM3D](https://aihabitat.org/datasets/hm3d/), "
"[MatterPort3D](https://niessner.github.io/Matterport/), "
"[Gibson](http://gibsonenv.stanford.edu/database/), etc. See "
"[here](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/tree/features/irsim/world/map/binary_map_generator_hm3d) for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"**可用地图**：我们在 `irsim/world/map` 文件夹中提供了一些示例地图，你也可以使用来自 "
"[HM3D](https://aihabitat.org/datasets/hm3d/)、[MatterPort3D](https://niessner.github.io/Matterport/)、[Gibson](http://gibsonenv.stanford.edu/database/)"
" 等 3D 数据集的自定义地图。更多细节见 [此处](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/tree/features/irsim/world/map/binary_map_generator_hm3d)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:579
msgid "**`mdownsample`** (`int`, default: `1`)"
msgstr "**`mdownsample`** (`int`, 默认值： `1`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:580
msgid "Sets the downsampling factor for the obstacle map image."
msgstr "设置障碍物地图图像的降采样系数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:582
msgid ""
"**Performance Tip**: A higher value reduces the resolution of the "
"obstacle map, which can optimize the simulation performance by decreasing"
" computational load."
msgstr "**提示**：更高的取值会降低障碍地图的分辨率，减小计算负载，从而提升仿真性能。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**world visualization**"
msgstr "**world 可视化**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:589
#, python-brace-format
msgid "**`plot`** (`dict`, default: `{}`)"
msgstr "**`plot`** (`dict`, 默认值： `{}`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:590
msgid "Specifies the plotting options for initializing the plot of the world."
msgstr "指定初始化世界绘图时可用的绘制选项。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:592
msgid "**Visualization Options:**"
msgstr "**可视化选项：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:593
msgid ""
"`saved_figure`: Default `dpi` is `100`; default format is `png`; default "
"bbox_inches is `tight`. See "
"[matplotlib.pyplot.savefig](https://matplotlib.org/stable/api/_as_gen/matplotlib.pyplot.savefig.html)"
" for more details."
msgstr ""
"`saved_figure`：默认 `dpi` 为 `100`；默认格式为 `png`；默认 bbox_inches 为 "
"`tight`。更多细节参见 "
"[matplotlib.pyplot.savefig](https://matplotlib.org/stable/api/_as_gen/matplotlib.pyplot.savefig.html)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:594
msgid ""
"`figure_pixels`: Width and height of the figure in pixels. Default is "
"`[1000, 800]`."
msgstr "`figure_pixels`: 图像的像素宽和高，默认值为`[1000, 800]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:595
msgid "`show_title`: Whether to show the plot title. Default is `True`."
msgstr "`show_title`: 是否显示图表标题，默认是`True`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:596
msgid ""
"`title`: Custom title for the plot. If not specified, shows simulation "
"time and status."
msgstr "`title`：自定义图表标题；若未指定，则显示仿真时间与当前状态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:597
msgid "`no_axis`: Whether to show the axis. Default is `False`."
msgstr "`no_axis`： 是否显示坐标轴，默认是`False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:598
msgid "`tight`: Whether to use tight layout. Default is `True`."
msgstr "`tight`: 是否使用紧凑布局，默认是`True`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:599
msgid ""
"`viewpoint`: Controls the center of the camera/viewport. Default is "
"`null`."
msgstr "`viewpoint`: 控制相机（视角）的中心位置，默认值为`null`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:600
msgid "`null`: Use the initial world bounds (no automatic panning)."
msgstr "`null`：使用初始的世界边界，不进行自动移动"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:601
msgid "`[x, y]`: Keep the viewport centered at the fixed point `[x, y]`."
msgstr "`[x, y]`：视角始终以固定点`[x, y]`为中心"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:602
msgid ""
"`\"<object_name>\"`: Follow the object with that name (dynamic panning), "
"e.g., `\"robot_0\"`."
msgstr "`\"<object_name>\"`：跟随该名称的对象进行动态平移，例如`\"robot_0\"`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:614
msgid "Complete World Configuration Example"
msgstr "完整世界配置示例"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:640
msgid ""
"**`obstacle_map`**: Replace `\"path/to/map.png\"` with the actual file "
"path to your obstacle map image. Ensure that the image is in a compatible"
" format (e.g., PNG, JPEG) and properly represents obstacle locations."
msgstr ""
"**`obstacle_map`**：将 `\"path/to/map.png\"` "
"替换为你的障碍物地图图像的实际文件路径。请确保图像为兼容格式（如 PNG、JPEG）并正确表示障碍物位置。"

