#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:690
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:955
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1127
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1181
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:692
msgid "**`number`** — How many objects to create"
msgstr "**`number`** — 创建多少个对象"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:693
msgid "**`distribution`** — Object placement (`manual`, `random`, `circle`)"
msgstr "**`distribution`** — 对象摆放位置分布 (`manual`, `random`, `circle`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:694
msgid "**`state`** — Initial position (`[x, y, θ]`)"
msgstr "**`state`** — 初始化位置 (`[x, y, θ]`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:695
msgid "**`goal`** — Target destination (`[x, y, θ]`)"
msgstr "**`goal`** — 目标位姿 (`[x, y, θ]`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:696
msgid "**`velocity`** — Initial speed (`[v, ω]`, `[forward, lateral]`, `[v, φ]`)"
msgstr "**`velocity`** — 初始化速度 (`[v, ω]`, `[forward, lateral]`, `[v, φ]`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:697
msgid "**`state_dim`** — State vector size (auto: 3 or 4)"
msgstr "**`state_dim`** — 状态向量维度 (auto: 3 或 4)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:698
msgid "**`vel_dim`** — Velocity vector size (auto: 2)"
msgstr "**`vel_dim`** — 速度向量维度 (auto: 2)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:699
msgid "**`name`** — Unique identifier for the object."
msgstr "**`name`** — 对象的唯一标识符"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:700
msgid "**`role`** — Object type (`robot`, `obstacle`)"
msgstr "**`role`** — 对象类型（`robot`、`obstacle`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:704
msgid "**`number`** (`int`, default: `1`)"
msgstr "**`number`** (`int`, 默认值： `1`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:705
msgid "Specifies the number of objects to create using the given configuration."
msgstr "指定使用该配置创建的对象数量。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:714
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**`distribution`** (`dict`, default: `{name: manual}`) ([source](https"
"://ir-"
"sim.readthedocs.io/en/dev/irsim.world.html#irsim.world.object_factory.ObjectFactory.generate_state_list))"
msgstr ""
"**`distribution`**（`dict`，默认值：`{name: manual}`）（[源码](https://ir-"
"sim.readthedocs.io/en/dev/irsim.world.html#irsim.world.object_factory.ObjectFactory.generate_state_list)）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:715
msgid ""
"Defines how multiple objects are spatially distributed when `number` is "
"greater than `1`."
msgstr "当`number`大于1时，定义多个对象在空间中的分布方式。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:718
msgid "`'manual'`: Manually specify initial states and goals for each object."
msgstr "`'manual'`:手动为每个对象指定初始状态和目标"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:719
msgid ""
"In this case, the `state` (or goal) parameters must be provided for each "
"object. If the provided list is shorter than the number of objects, the "
"last state (or goal) is repeated."
msgstr "这种模式下必须为每个对象提供`state`（或目标）参数；如果提供的列表长度少于对象数量，则最后一个状态（或目标）会被重复使用。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:728
msgid ""
"`'random'`: Randomly distribute objects within specified ranges. Points "
"are rejection-sampled so every pair is at least `min_distance` apart in "
"the xy plane. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'random'`: 在指定范围内随机分布对象。采样过程采用拒绝采样，保证任意两点在 xy 平面上的距离至少为 "
"`min_distance`。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:729
msgid ""
"`range_low` (list): Lower bounds `[x, y, theta]` for random distribution."
" Defaults to the world bounds inset by `0.5`, i.e. `[offset_x + 0.5, "
"offset_y + 0.5, -pi]`."
msgstr ""
"`range_low` (list): 随机分布的下界 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为世界边界向内缩进 `0.5`，即 "
"`[offset_x + 0.5, offset_y + 0.5, -pi]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:730
msgid ""
"`range_high` (list): Upper bounds `[x, y, theta]` for random "
"distribution. Defaults to `[offset_x + width - 0.5, offset_y + height - "
"0.5, pi]`."
msgstr ""
"`range_high` (list): 随机分布的上界 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为 `[offset_x + width - "
"0.5, offset_y + height - 0.5, pi]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:731
msgid ""
"`min_distance` (float): Minimum pairwise xy distance between sampled "
"points. Default is `1.0`."
msgstr "`min_distance` (float): 采样点之间在 xy 平面上的最小两两距离。默认值为 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:738
msgid ""
"`'circle'`: Arrange objects in a circular formation around a specified "
"center. Optional parameters:"
msgstr "`'circle'`:将对象以圆形阵列排布在指定中心周围。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:739
msgid ""
"`center` (list): Center coordinates `[x, y, theta]` of the circle. "
"Defaults to the world center `[offset_x + width / 2, offset_y + height / "
"2, 0]`."
msgstr ""
"`center` (list): 圆心坐标 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为世界中心 `[offset_x + width / 2, "
"offset_y + height / 2, 0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:740
msgid ""
"`radius` (float): Radius of the circle. Defaults to `min(width, height) /"
" 2 - 0.5` so the circle sits inside the world with a small margin."
msgstr "`radius` (float): 圆的半径。默认值为 `min(width, height) / 2 - 0.5`，使圆形排布留有少量边距。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:748
msgid "**`state`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[0, 0, 0]`)"
msgstr "**`state`** (`float`列表, 默认为`[0, 0, 0]`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:749
msgid ""
"Defines the initial state of the object, typically in the format `[x, y, "
"theta]`, where `theta` represents the orientation in radians. If the "
"provided state has more elements than required, extra elements are "
"truncated; if fewer, missing values are filled with zeros."
msgstr ""
"定义对象的初始状态，通常为 `[x, y, theta]` 格式，其中 `theta` "
"表示以弧度为单位的朝向。若提供的状态元素多于所需，多余的会被截断；若不足，缺失值以零补齐。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:757
msgid "**`velocity`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[0] * action_dim`)"
msgstr "**`velocity`**（`float` 列表，默认：`[0] * action_dim`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:758
msgid ""
"Specifies the initial velocity (list) of the object. The length must "
"match the kinematics action dimension. The format depends on the "
"kinematics model:"
msgstr "指定对象的初始速度（列表）。长度须与运动学动作维度匹配。格式取决于运动学模型："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:760
msgid "**Format by Kinematics:**"
msgstr "**运动学模型的格式：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:761
msgid ""
"For `'diff'`: `[v, omega]`, where `v` is linear velocity and `omega` is "
"angular velocity."
msgstr "`'diff'`模型参数由`[v, omega]`构成， 其中 `v` 线速度，`omega`角速度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:762
msgid ""
"For `'omni'`: `[forward, lateral]`, body-frame velocities (forward and "
"lateral relative to heading)."
msgstr "`'omni'`模型参数由`[forward, lateral]`构成，为机体坐标系下的速度（相对于朝向的前进和横向速度）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:763
msgid ""
"For `'acker'`: Typically `[v, phi]`, where `v` is linear velocity and "
"`phi` is steering angle."
msgstr "`'acker'`模型参数通常由`[v, phi]`构成，其中 `v` 是线速度，`phi`是转向角。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:771
msgid ""
"**`goal`** (`list` of `float` or `list` of `list` of `float`, default: "
"`None`)"
msgstr "**`goal`** (`float` 列表或 `float` 列表的列表，默认值：`None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:772
msgid ""
"Sets the target state or position the object should move toward. Used in "
"conjunction with behaviors to guide the object's navigation. The format "
"is `[x, y, theta]` or `[[x, y, theta], [x, y, theta], ...]` for multiple "
"goals."
msgstr ""
"设置对象应移动到的目标状态或位置。与行为配合使用以引导对象导航。格式为 `[x, y, theta]`，或多目标时为 `[[x, y, "
"theta], [x, y, theta], ...]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:779
msgid ""
"**Note**: For multiple goals for the single object (Pay attention to the "
"difference between the single goal for multiple objects and multiple "
"goals for the single object):"
msgstr "**注意**：对于单个对象的多个目标（注意区分多个对象的单个目标与单个对象的多个目标）："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:788
msgid "**`state_dim`** (`int`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`state_dim`** (`int`, 默认值： `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:789
msgid ""
"Explicitly defines the dimension of the state vector. When not specified,"
" this is automatically inferred from the kinematics model. For most use "
"cases, the default inference is sufficient."
msgstr "显式定义状态向量的维度。若未指定，则自动从运动学模型推断。对于大多数使用场景，默认推断即可满足需求。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:791
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:804
msgid "**Common Values:**"
msgstr "**常用值：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:792
msgid "`3`: For 2D position and orientation `[x, y, theta]`"
msgstr "`3`: 2D的位置和朝向角 `[x, y, theta]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:793
msgid ""
"`4`: For vehicles with additional state (e.g., Ackermann with `[x, y, "
"theta, steer_angle]`)"
msgstr "`4`：对于具有额外状态的车辆（例如 Ackermann 模型的`[x, y, theta, steer_angle]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:801
msgid "**`vel_dim`** (`int`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`vel_dim`** (`int`, 默认值： `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:802
msgid ""
"Explicitly defines the dimension of the velocity vector. When not "
"specified, this is automatically inferred from the kinematics model. The "
"velocity dimension depends on the control inputs for the specific "
"kinematics."
msgstr "显式定义速度向量的维度。若未指定，则自动从运动学模型推断。速度维度取决于特定运动学模型的控制输入。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:805
msgid ""
"`2`: For differential drive `[v, omega]` or omnidirectional `[forward, "
"lateral]`"
msgstr "`2`：对于差速驱动`[v, omega]`或全向 `[forward, lateral]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:806
msgid ""
"`3`: For omnidirectional with angular control `[forward, lateral, "
"yaw_rate]`"
msgstr "`3`：对于带角速度控制的全向模型 `[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:814
msgid "**`group`** (`int`, default: `0`)"
msgstr "**`group`**（`int`，默认 `0`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:815
msgid ""
"Specifies a group identifier for organizational purposes, allowing "
"objects to be categorized and managed together. Objects with the same "
"group ID can be treated as a cohesive unit for certain operations."
msgstr "指定用于组织目的的分组标识符，允许对象被分类和管理。具有相同分组 ID 的对象可作为一个整体用于某些操作。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:823
msgid "**`group_name`** (`str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`group_name`** (`str`, 默认值为: `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:824
msgid ""
"Specifies a group name for organizational purposes, allowing objects to "
"be categorized and managed together. Objects with the same group name can"
" be treated as a cohesive unit for certain operations."
msgstr "用于组织目的指定分组名称，使对象能够被分类并统一管理。具有相同分组名称的对象在某些操作中可作为一个整体进行处理。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:832
msgid "**`name`** (`str` or `list` of `str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`name`**（`str` 或 `str` 列表，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:833
msgid ""
"Sets a unique identifier for the object. If not provided, the name "
"defaults to \"<role>_<id>\" (e.g., `robot_0`, `obstacle_3`). Names must "
"be unique across all objects in the environment; duplicates will raise a "
"`ValueError` during initialization."
msgstr ""
"为对象设置唯一标识符。若未提供，名称默认为 \"<role>_<id>\"（例如 "
"`robot_0`、`obstacle_3`）。名称在环境中所有对象间必须唯一；重复会在初始化时抛出 `ValueError`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:835
msgid ""
"When creating multiple objects (`number > 1`), you can provide a list of "
"names. If the provided list is shorter than the number of objects, the "
"last name is repeated for remaining objects; ensure uniqueness to avoid "
"errors."
msgstr "创建多个对象（`number > 1`）时，可提供名称列表。若列表长度小于对象数量，则最后一个名称会被重复使用；请确保名称唯一性以避免错误。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:858
msgid ""
"Do not confuse the object-level `name` with the `name` keys inside "
"dictionaries like `shape`, `kinematics`, or `behavior`. The latter "
"specify the type of that component, not the object's identifier."
msgstr ""
"请勿将对象级 `name` 与 `shape`、`kinematics`、`behavior` 等字典内部的 `name` "
"键混淆。后者指定该组件的类型，而非对象的标识符。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:861
msgid "**`role`** (`str`, default: `'obstacle'`)"
msgstr "**`role`** (`str`, 默认值： `'obstacle'`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:862
msgid ""
"Defines the object's role in the simulation, determined by the section it"
" belongs to:"
msgstr "定义对象在仿真中的角色，由其所属的配置区块决定："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:863
msgid ""
"`'robot'`: An active entity typically controlled by behaviors or input "
"commands."
msgstr "`'robot'`：主动实体，通常由行为或输入命令控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:864
msgid ""
"`'obstacle'`: A passive entity that may or may not move but is considered"
" during collision detection."
msgstr "`'obstacle'`：被动实体，可静止也可移动，但参与碰撞检测。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object kinematics**"
msgstr "**object 运动学**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:870
msgid "Kinematics Models"
msgstr "运动学模型"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:872
msgid ""
"**`diff`** — Differential drive, controlled by linear speed and angular "
"velocity (`[v, omega]`)"
msgstr "**`diff`** — 差速驱动，由线速度和角速度控制（`[v, omega]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:873
msgid ""
"**`omni`** — Omnidirectional, controlled by body-frame forward and "
"lateral speed (`[forward, lateral]`)"
msgstr "**`omni`** — 全向移动，由机体坐标系下的前进和横向速度控制（`[forward, lateral]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:874
msgid ""
"**`omni_angular`** — Omnidirectional with angular control, controlled by "
"body-frame speeds and yaw rate (`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`)"
msgstr ""
"**`omni_angular`** — 带角速度控制的全向移动，由机体坐标系下的速度和偏航角速度控制（`[forward, lateral, "
"yaw_rate]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:875
msgid ""
"**`acker`** — Ackermann steering, controlled by linear speed and steering"
" angle (`[v, phi]`)"
msgstr "**`acker`** — 阿克曼转向，由线速度和转向角控制（`[v, phi]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:879
msgid "**`kinematics`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`kinematics`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:880
msgid "Sets the kinematic model governing the object's movement."
msgstr "设置控制对象运动的运动学模型。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:883
msgid ""
"`'diff'`: Differential drive robot, suitable for robots that can rotate "
"in place (e.g., two-wheel robots). This type of robot is controlled by "
"linear and angular velocity. Optional parameters:"
msgstr "`'diff'`：差速驱动机器人，适用于原地旋转的机器人（如两轮机器人）。通过线速度和角速度控制。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:884
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:893
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:902
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:911
msgid ""
"`noise` (bool): whether to add noise to the velocity commands. Default is"
" `False`."
msgstr "`noise`（bool）：是否给速度命令添加噪声。默认为 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:885
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:912
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands. Default is "
"`[0.03, 0, 0, 0.03]`."
msgstr "`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数。默认值为 `[0.03, 0, 0, 0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:892
msgid ""
"`'omni'`: Omnidirectional movement, allowing movement in any direction "
"without changing orientation. This type of robot is controlled by body-"
"frame velocities `[forward, lateral]`. Orientation (theta) is preserved "
"but not updated. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'omni'`：全向运动，允许在任意方向移动而不改变朝向。此类机器人通过机体坐标系速度 `[forward, lateral]` "
"控制。朝向角（theta）保持不变。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:894
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands `[alpha_forward, "
"alpha_lateral]`. Default is `[0.03, 0.03]`."
msgstr ""
"`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数 `[alpha_forward, alpha_lateral]`。默认值为 `[0.03, "
"0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:901
msgid ""
"`'omni_angular'`: Omnidirectional movement with angular velocity control."
" Extends `omni` by adding a yaw rate channel that integrates orientation "
"(theta). This type of robot is controlled by body-frame velocities "
"`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'omni_angular'`：带角速度控制的全向运动。在 `omni` "
"基础上增加偏航角速度通道以积分朝向角（theta）。此类机器人通过机体坐标系速度 `[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]` "
"控制。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:903
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands `[alpha_forward, "
"alpha_lateral, alpha_yaw]`. Default is `[0.03, 0.03, 0.03]`."
msgstr ""
"`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数 `[alpha_forward, alpha_lateral, alpha_yaw]`。默认值为 "
"`[0.03, 0.03, 0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:910
msgid ""
"`'acker'`: Ackermann steering, typical for car-like vehicles requiring a "
"turning radius."
msgstr "`'acker'`：阿克曼转向，典型用于类车辆，需要转向半径。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:913
msgid ""
"`mode` (str): steering mode, either `steer` or `angular`. Default is "
"`steer`."
msgstr "`mode`（str）：转向模式，为 `steer` 或 `angular`。默认为 `steer`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:914
msgid "`steer`: the object is controlled by linear and steer angle."
msgstr "`steer`：对象通过线速度和转向角控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:915
msgid "`angular`: the object is controlled by linear and angular velocity."
msgstr "`angular`：对象通过线速度和角速度控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:923
msgid ""
"**`vel_min`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[-1, -1]`) and **`vel_max`** "
"(`list` of `float`, default: `[1, 1]`)"
msgstr ""
"**`vel_min`**（`float` 列表，默认值：`[-1, -1]`）和 **`vel_max`**（`float` "
"列表，默认值：`[1, 1]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:924
msgid ""
"Set the minimum and maximum velocity limits for each control dimension "
"(e.g., linear and angular velocities). These constraints ensure the "
"object's motion stays within feasible and safe bounds."
msgstr "设置每个控制维度的最小和最大速度限制（例如线速度和角速度）。这些约束确保对象的运动保持在可行且安全的范围内。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:927
msgid "**`acce`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[inf, inf]`)"
msgstr "**`acce`**（`float` 列表，默认值：`[inf, inf]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:928
msgid ""
"Defines acceleration limits as the maximum change in velocity per time "
"step for each control dimension. This parameter simulates the physical "
"limitations of the object's motion capabilities."
msgstr "定义加速度限制，即每个控制维度在每个时间步内的最大速度变化。此参数模拟对象运动能力的物理限制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:931
msgid "**`angle_range`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[-pi, pi]`)"
msgstr "**`angle_range`**（`float` 列表，默认：`[-pi, pi]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:932
msgid ""
"Specifies the allowed range of orientation angles `[min, max]` in "
"radians. The object's orientation angle `theta` is wrapped within this "
"range to maintain consistency."
msgstr "指定允许的朝向角范围 `[min, max]`（弧度）。对象的朝向角 `theta` 会被归整到此范围内以保持一致性。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:935
msgid "**`goal_threshold`** (`float`, default: `0.1`)"
msgstr "**`goal_threshold`**（`float`，默认：`0.1`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:936
msgid ""
"Determines the proximity threshold to the goal at which the object is "
"considered to have arrived. Once within this distance, arrival behaviors "
"or state changes may be triggered."
msgstr "确定对象被认为已到达目标的距离阈值。一旦在此距离范围内，可能会触发到达行为或状态变化。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:948
msgid ""
"When using the `acker` kinematics model, ensure that the `wheelbase` "
"parameter is set in the `shape` configuration."
msgstr "使用 `acker` 运动学模型时，请确保在 `shape` 配置中设置 `wheelbase` 参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object shape**"
msgstr "**object 形状**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:957
msgid "**`circle`** — Round shape (`radius`, `center`)"
msgstr "**`circle`** — 圆形（`radius`、`center`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:958
msgid "**`rectangle`** — Rectangular shape (`length`, `width`, `wheelbase`)"
msgstr "**`rectangle`** — 矩形（`length`、`width`、`wheelbase`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:959
msgid "**`polygon`** — Custom shape (`vertices`, `is_convex`)"
msgstr "**`polygon`** — 自定义多边形（`vertices`、`is_convex`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:960
msgid "**`linestring`** — Line segments (`vertices`)"
msgstr "**`linestring`** — 线段（`vertices`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:964
#, python-brace-format
msgid "**`shape`** (`dict`, default: `{name: circle}`)"
msgstr "**`shape`**（`dict`，默认 `{name: circle}`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:965
msgid ""
"Determines the geometric shape used for collision detection and "
"visualization in the original state."
msgstr "决定用于碰撞检测与可视化的几何形状。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:967
msgid "**Supported Shapes:**"
msgstr "**支持的形状：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:969
msgid "**`'circle'`**: Represents a circular shape."
msgstr "**`'circle'`**：圆形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:970
msgid "**`radius`** (`float`): Radius of the circle. Default is `0.2`."
msgstr "**`radius`**（`float`）：圆半径，默认 `0.2`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:971
msgid "**`center`** (`list`): Center (x, y) of the circle. Default is `[0, 0]`."
msgstr "**`center`**（列表）：圆心 (x, y)，默认 `[0, 0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:972
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a random radius. Default"
" is `False`."
msgstr "**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否随机半径，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:973
msgid ""
"**`radius_range`** (`list`): Range `[min_radius, max_radius]` for random "
"radius generation if `random_shape` is `True`. Default is `[0.1, 1.0]`."
msgstr ""
"**`radius_range`**（`list`）：当 `random_shape` 为 `True` 时用于随机半径生成的范围 "
"`[min_radius, max_radius]`。默认值为 `[0.1, 1.0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:974
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:984
msgid ""
"**`wheelbase`** (`float`): Wheelbase of the Ackermann steering vehicle. "
"Required when using `'acker'` kinematics. Default is `None`."
msgstr "**`wheelbase`**（`float`）：阿克曼转向车辆的轴距，使用 `'acker'` 时必填，默认 `None`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:981
msgid "**`'rectangle'`**: Represents a rectangular shape."
msgstr "**`'rectangle'`**：矩形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:982
msgid ""
"**`length`** (`float`): Length of the rectangle along the x-axis. Default"
" is `1.0`."
msgstr "**`length`**（`float`）：x 轴方向长度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:983
msgid ""
"**`width`** (`float`): Width of the rectangle along the y-axis. Default "
"is `1.0`."
msgstr "**`width`**（`float`）：y 轴方向宽度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:991
msgid ""
"**`'polygon'`**: Represents a polygonal shape defined by a list of "
"vertices."
msgstr "**`'polygon'`**：由顶点列表定义的多边形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:992
msgid ""
"**`vertices`** (`list`): List of vertices defining the polygon in the "
"format `[[x1, y1], [x2, y2], ...]`, if not provided, a random polygon "
"will be generated."
msgstr "**`vertices`**（列表）：定义多边形的顶点列表，格式 `[[x1, y1], ...]`。若未提供则生成随机多边形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:993
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random "
"polygons. Default is `False`."
msgstr "**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否生成一系列随机多边形，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:994
msgid ""
"**`is_convex`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random convex "
"polygons. Default is `False`."
msgstr "**`is_convex`**（`bool`）：是否生成一系列随机凸多边形，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:995
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"parameters for random polygon generation, see "
"{py:func}`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon` for "
"more details. Parameters include `number `, `center_range `, "
"`avg_radius_range `, `irregularity_range `, `spikeyness_range `, "
"`num_vertices_range `."
msgstr ""
"随机多边形生成的参数，更多细节参见 "
"{py:func}`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon`。参数包括 "
"`number `、`center_range `、`avg_radius_range `、`irregularity_range "
"`、`spikeyness_range `、`num_vertices_range `。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1014
msgid ""
"**`'linestring'`**: Represents a line string shape defined by a list of "
"vertices. Similar to a polygon but generates a line string."
msgstr "**`'linestring'`**：由顶点列表定义的折线，类似多边形但生成的是一串线。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1015
msgid ""
"**`vertices`** (`list`): List of vertices defining the line string in the"
" format `[[x1, y1], [x2, y2], ...]`."
msgstr "**`vertices`**（列表）：定义线串的顶点列表，格式 `[[x1, y1], ...]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1016
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random line "
"strings (polygon). Default is `False`."
msgstr "**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否生成随机线串（多边形），默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1017
msgid ""
"**`is_convex`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random convex "
"line strings (polygons). Default is `True`."
msgstr "**`is_convex`**（`bool`）：是否生成随机凸线串（多边形），默认 `True`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1018
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"parameters for random line string generation (polygon), see "
"{py:func}`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon` for "
"more details. Parameters include `number `, `center_range `, "
"`avg_radius_range `, `irregularity_range `, `spikeyness_range `, "
"`num_vertices_range `."
msgstr ""
"随机折线（多边形）生成的参数，更多细节参见 "
"{py:func}`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon`。参数包括 "
"`number `、`center_range `、`avg_radius_range `、`irregularity_range "
"`、`spikeyness_range `、`num_vertices_range `。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object behavior**"
msgstr "**object 行为**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1041
msgid "Behavior Systems"
msgstr "行为系统"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1043
msgid ""
"**`behavior`**: `dash` (move toward the goal directly), `rvo` (collision "
"avoidance algorithm)"
msgstr "**`behavior`**：`dash`（直接朝目标移动）、`rvo`（碰撞避让算法）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1044
msgid "**`group_behavior`**: `orca` (optimal reciprocal collision avoidance)"
msgstr "**`group_behavior`**：`orca`（最优互惠碰撞避免）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1045
msgid "**`static`** — Immobile objects (`True`/`False`)"
msgstr "**`static`** — 静止对象（`True`/`False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1049
msgid "**`behavior`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`behavior`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1050
msgid ""
"Configures the movement behavior of the object. Behaviors can be simple "
"or complex and may include additional parameters."
msgstr "配置对象的运动行为，可为简单或复杂策略，并可包含额外参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1053
msgid "`'dash'`: Moves directly toward the goal at maximum allowable speed."
msgstr "`'dash'`：以最大允许速度直接朝目标移动。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1054
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1067
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1093
msgid ""
"`wander` (bool/`False`): Whether to add random wandering to the movement."
" If `True`, the object will have a random goal when reach current goal."
msgstr "`wander`（bool/`False`）：是否加入随机游走。若为 `True`，对象到达当前目标后会随机分配新目标。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1055
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1068
msgid ""
"`loop` (bool/`False`): Whether to loop through waypoints continuously. If"
" `True`, the object will restart from the first waypoint after reaching "
"the last one."
msgstr "`loop`（bool/`False`）：是否循环导航路径点。若为 `True`，对象到达最后一个路径点后会从第一个路径点重新开始。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1056
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1069
msgid ""
"`target_roles` (str/`all`): Only the objects with the target role will be"
" applied to the behavior. Currently, you can set the target role as "
"`robot` or `obstacle`."
msgstr "`target_roles`（str/`all`）：仅对具有目标角色的对象应用该行为。当前可设为 `robot` 或 `obstacle`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1057
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1070
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1094
msgid "`range_low`(list/`[0, 0, -3.14]`): Lower bounds for random wandering."
msgstr "`range_low`（列表）：随机游走下界，默认 `[0, 0, -3.14]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1058
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1071
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1095
msgid "`range_high`(list/`[10, 10, 3.14]`): Upper bounds for random wandering."
msgstr "`range_high`（列表）：随机游走上界，默认 `[10, 10, 3.14]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1059
msgid ""
"`angle_tolerance` (float/`0.1`): Tolerance for orientation alignment with"
" `diff`, `acker`, and `omni_angular` kinematics."
msgstr ""
"`angle_tolerance`（float）：`diff`、`acker`、`omni_angular` 运动学的朝向校准容差，默认 "
"`0.1`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1061
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1082
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1103
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1118
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1151
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1171
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1195
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1204
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1229
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1245
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1319
msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1066
msgid ""
"`'rvo'`: Implements Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles for collision avoidance"
" among multiple moving objects. Support kinematics are `diff` and `omni`."
msgstr "`'rvo'`：实现多动态体避碰的 RVO 算法，支持 `diff` 与 `omni` 运动学。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1072
msgid "`vxmax` (float/`1.5`): Maximum linear velocity in x axis."
msgstr "`vxmax`（float）：x 轴最大线速度，默认 `1.5`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1073
msgid "`vymax` (float/`1.5`): Maximum linear velocity in y axis."
msgstr "`vymax`（float）：y 轴最大线速度，默认 `1.5`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1074
msgid "`acce` (float/`1.0`): Maximum acceleration."
msgstr "`acce`（float）：最大加速度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1075
msgid "`factor` (float/`1.0`): Factor for the RVO algorithm."
msgstr "`factor`（float）：RVO 算法因子，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1076
msgid "`mode` (str/`rvo`): Mode for RVO algorithm, either `rvo`, `hrvo`, or `vo`."
msgstr "`mode`（str）：RVO 算法模式，可选 `rvo`、`hrvo`、`vo`，默认 `rvo`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1077
msgid "`rvo`: Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles. For multi-agent collision avoidance."
msgstr "`rvo`：互惠速度障碍法，用于多智能体避碰。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1078
msgid ""
"`hrvo`: Hybrid Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles. Combine RVO with VO to "
"avoid deadlocks."
msgstr "`hrvo`：混合 RVO，将 RVO 与 VO 结合以减少死锁。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1079
msgid "`vo`: Velocity Obstacles. For obstacle avoidance."
msgstr "`vo`：速度障碍，用于避障。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1080
msgid ""
"`neighbor_threshold` (float/`3.0`): Distance threshold to filter the "
"neighbors to the self robot."
msgstr "`neighbor_threshold`（float）：筛选邻居的距离阈值，默认 `3.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1088
msgid "**`group_behavior`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`group_behavior`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1089
msgid ""
"Group-level behavior for all objects within the same group. This is more "
"efficient for coordinated behaviors (like swarm or crowd simulation) as "
"it computes actions for all members in a single step. Must include `name`"
" plus behavior-specific parameters."
msgstr "同组内所有对象的群体行为。对于协同行为（如群体或人群仿真）更高效，因为它在单步中为所有成员计算动作。必须包含 `name` 及行为特定参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1092
msgid ""
"`'orca'`: Optimal Reciprocal Collision Avoidance (ORCA) for multi-agent "
"navigation. Requires `pyrvo` package (`pip install pyrvo`). The "
"simulation will attempt to import it only when this behavior is used."
msgstr ""
"`'orca'`：用于多智能体导航的最优互惠碰撞避免（ORCA）。需要 `pyrvo` 包（`pip install "
"pyrvo`）。仅在使用该行为时仿真才会尝试导入它。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1096
msgid "`neighborDist` (float/`15.0`): Max distance to search for neighbors."
msgstr "`neighborDist`（float/`15.0`）：搜索邻居的最大距离。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1097
msgid "`maxNeighbors` (int/`10`): Max number of neighbors to consider."
msgstr "`maxNeighbors`（int/`10`）：考虑的邻居数量上限。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1098
msgid ""
"`timeHorizon` (float/`20.0`): Time horizon for computing safe velocities "
"with respect to other agents."
msgstr "`timeHorizon`（float/`20.0`）：相对于其他智能体计算安全速度的时间范围。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1099
msgid ""
"`timeHorizonObst` (float/`10.0`): Time horizon for computing safe "
"velocities with respect to static obstacles."
msgstr "`timeHorizonObst`（float/`10.0`）：相对于静态障碍物计算安全速度的时间范围。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1100
msgid "`safe_radius` (float/`0.1`): Additional safety radius padding."
msgstr "`safe_radius`（float/`0.1`）：额外的安全半径填充。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1101
msgid ""
"`maxSpeed` (float/`None`): Max speed for the agents. If `None`, uses the "
"object's `vel_max`."
msgstr "`maxSpeed`（float/`None`）：智能体最大速度。若为 `None`，使用对象的 `vel_max`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1115
msgid ""
"**`static`**:   A boolean indicating whether the object is static (does "
"not move). Static objects ignore kinematics and behaviors, remaining at "
"their initial state."
msgstr "**`static`**：布尔值，表示对象是否静止。静止对象忽略运动学与行为，保持初始状态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object sensors**"
msgstr "**object 传感器**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1129
msgid "**`lidar2d`** — 2D laser scanner (`range_min/max`, `angle_range`, `noise`)"
msgstr "**`lidar2d`** — 2D 激光雷达（`range_min/max`、`angle_range`、`noise`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1130
msgid "**`fov`** — Field of view angle (radians)"
msgstr "**`fov`** — 视场角（弧度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1131
msgid "**`fov_radius`** — Maximum detection distance"
msgstr "**`fov_radius`** — 最大探测距离"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1135
msgid ""
"**`sensors`**:   Attaches sensors to the object for environmental "
"perception. Each sensor is defined by a dictionary indicating its type "
"and specific parameters. Currently supported sensor `name` (or `type`) "
"include:"
msgstr "**`sensors`**：为对象挂载传感器以感知环境。每个传感器以字典形式描述其类型与参数，目前支持："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1137
msgid "`lidar2d`: 2D LiDAR sensor for distance measurements. Parameters include:"
msgstr "`lidar2d`：用于距离测量的 2D LiDAR，参数包括："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1138
msgid "`range_min` (float/`0.0`): Minimum detection range."
msgstr "`range_min`（float）：最小探测距离，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1139
msgid "`range_max` (float/`10.0`): Maximum detection range."
msgstr "`range_max`（float）：最大探测距离，默认 `10.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1140
msgid "`angle_range` (float/`pi`): Total angle range of the sensor."
msgstr "`angle_range`（float）：传感器覆盖角度，默认 `pi`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1141
msgid "`number` (int/`100`): Number of laser beams."
msgstr "`number`（int）：激光束数量，默认 `100`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1142
msgid "`scan_time` (float/`0.1`): Time taken for one complete scan."
msgstr "`scan_time`（float）：完成一次扫描的时间，默认 `0.1`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1143
msgid "`noise` (bool/`False`): Whether noise is added to measurements."
msgstr "`noise`（bool）：测量是否加入噪声，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1144
msgid ""
"`std` (float/`0.2`): Standard deviation for range noise if `noise` is "
"`True`."
msgstr "`std`（float）：当 `noise=True` 时距离噪声的标准差，默认 `0.2`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1145
msgid ""
"`angle_std` (float/`0.02`): Standard deviation for angle noise if `noise`"
" is `True`."
msgstr "`angle_std`（float）：`noise=True` 时的角度噪声标准差，默认 `0.02`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1146
msgid ""
"`offset` (list/`[0, 0, 0]`): Offset of the sensor from the object's "
"position (x, y, theta)."
msgstr "`offset`（列表）：传感器相对对象位置 (x, y, theta) 的偏移，默认 `[0, 0, 0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1147
msgid "`alpha` (float/`0.3`): Transparency for plotting."
msgstr "`alpha`（float）：绘图透明度，默认 `0.3`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1148
msgid "`has_velocity` (bool/`False`): Whether measures the lidar point velocity."
msgstr "`has_velocity`（bool）：是否测量点速度，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1149
msgid "`color` (str/`r`): Color of the sensor."
msgstr "`color`（str）：传感器颜色，默认 `r`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1168
msgid ""
"**`fov`** and **`fov_radius`**:   Define the field of view (FOV) for the "
"object's sensors. The FOV is the angular range within which the sensor "
"can detect objects. The `fov` parameter specifies the angular range in "
"radians, while `fov_radius` sets the maximum detection distance."
msgstr ""
"**`fov`** 和 **`fov_radius`**：定义对象传感器的视场（FOV）。FOV 是传感器可检测对象的角度范围。`fov` "
"参数以弧度指定角度范围，`fov_radius` 设置最大检测距离。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object mode**"
msgstr "**object 模式**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1183
msgid "**`arrive_mode`** — Goal detection (`position`, `state`)"
msgstr "**`arrive_mode`** — 目标判定方式（`position`、`state`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1184
msgid "**`unobstructed`** — Ignore collisions (`True`/`False`)"
msgstr "**`unobstructed`** — 忽略碰撞（`True`/`False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1188
msgid "**`arrive_mode`** (`str`, default: `'position'`)"
msgstr "**`arrive_mode`**（`str`，默认 `'position'`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1189
msgid "Chooses the method for determining if the object has arrived at its goal:"
msgstr "选择判定对象是否到达目标的方法："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1192
msgid ""
"`'position'`: Arrival is based solely on proximity to the goal position "
"(`[x, y]`)."
msgstr "`'position'`：仅根据与目标位置 (`[x, y]`) 的距离判断。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1193
msgid ""
"`'state'`: Considers both position and orientation in the arrival check "
"(`[x, y, theta]`)."
msgstr "`'state'`：同时考虑位置与朝向 (`[x, y, theta]`)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1201
msgid "**`unobstructed`** (`bool`, default: `False`)"
msgstr "**`unobstructed`**（`bool`，默认 `False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1202
msgid ""
"When set to `True`, this object is treated as having an unobstructed "
"path, ignoring collisions with other objects and obstacles. This can be "
"useful for testing or for objects that must not be impeded."
msgstr "当设为 `True` 时，该对象被视为无障碍，忽略与其他对象和障碍物的碰撞，适合测试或需要不被阻挡的对象。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**object visualization**"
msgstr "**object 可视化**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1215
msgid "**`color`** — Object color (`'r'`, `'blue'`, `'k'`)"
msgstr "**`color`** — 对象颜色（`'r'`、`'blue'`、`'k'` 等）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1216
msgid "**`description`** — Image file (`'car_blue.png'`, `'diff_robot0.png'`)"
msgstr "**`description`** — 图像文件（如 `'car_blue.png'`、`'diff_robot0.png'`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1217
msgid "**`plot`** — Advanced display options"
msgstr "**`plot`** — 进阶显示选项"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1218
msgid "**Object** — Appearance (`obj_color`, `obj_alpha`, `obj_linestyle`)"
msgstr "**Object** — 外观（`obj_color`、`obj_alpha`、`obj_linestyle`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1219
msgid "**Goal** — Goal markers (`show_goal`, `goal_color`, `show_goal_text`)"
msgstr "**Goal** — 目标标记（`show_goal`、`goal_color`、`show_goal_text`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1220
msgid "**Trail** — Object trails (`show_trail`, `keep_trail_length`)"
msgstr "**Trail** — 轨迹点（`show_trail`、`keep_trail_length`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1221
msgid "**Trajectory** — Path lines (`show_trajectory`, `keep_traj_length`)"
msgstr "**Trajectory** — 路径线（`show_trajectory`、`keep_traj_length`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1222
msgid "**Sensors** — Sensor display (`show_sensor`, `show_fov`)"
msgstr "**Sensors** — 传感器显示（`show_sensor`、`show_fov`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1226
msgid "**`color`** (`str`, default: `'k'` (black))"
msgstr "**`color`**（`str`，默认 `'k'` 黑色）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1227
msgid ""
"Specifies the object's color in visualizations for easy identification. "
"Detailed color options can be found in [matplotlib "
"color](https://matplotlib.org/stable/gallery/color/named_colors.html)."
msgstr ""
"指定对象在可视化中的颜色以便于识别。详细的颜色选项见 [matplotlib "
"颜色](https://matplotlib.org/stable/gallery/color/named_colors.html)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1235
msgid "**`description`** (`str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`description`**（`str`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1236
msgid ""
"Provides an image for representing the object graphically. Supports image"
" files located in world/description. You can also set the absolute path "
"of the image file by your need."
msgstr "提供用于图形展示的图像，可使用 world/description 下的文件，或自定义绝对路径。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1238
msgid "**Available Images:**"
msgstr "**可用图像：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1239
msgid "`car_green.png`: A default image for the ackermann steering vehicle."
msgstr "`car_green.png`：阿克曼车辆默认图。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1240
msgid "`car_blue.png`"
msgstr "`car_blue.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1241
msgid "`car_red.png`"
msgstr "`car_red.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1242
msgid "`diff_robot0.png`"
msgstr "`diff_robot0.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1243
msgid "`diff_robot1.png`"
msgstr "`diff_robot1.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1251
msgid ""
"**`plot`**:   Contains plotting options controlling the visual "
"representation of the object. All plot elements are initially created at "
"the origin and positioned using transforms and data updates during "
"animation updates."
msgstr "**`plot`**：包含控制对象显示的绘图选项。所有绘图元素初始创建在原点，并在动画更新时通过变换与数据更新定位。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1254
msgid "**Object Visualization Properties:**"
msgstr "**对象可视化属性：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1255
msgid ""
"`obj_linestyle` (str/`'-'`): Line style for object outline (e.g., '-', "
"'--', ':', '-.')."
msgstr "`obj_linestyle`（str）：对象轮廓线型（如 '-', '--', ':', '-.'），默认 '-'."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1256
msgid ""
"`obj_zorder` (int/`3`): Z-order (drawing layer) for object elements. "
"Default is 3 for robots, 1 for obstacles."
msgstr "`obj_zorder`（int）：对象元素的绘制层级，机器人默认 3、障碍物默认 1。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1257
msgid ""
"`obj_color` (str): Color of the object. Default is the object's color "
"property."
msgstr "`obj_color`（str）：对象颜色，默认沿用 `color`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1258
msgid "`obj_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the object (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`obj_alpha`（float）：对象透明度（0.0-1.0），默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1259
msgid ""
"`obj_linewidth` (float/`None`): Width of the object outline. Default "
"varies by object type."
msgstr "`obj_linewidth`（float）：轮廓线宽，默认随对象类型而定。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1261
msgid "**Goal Visualization:**"
msgstr "**目标可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1262
msgid "`show_goal` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the goal position."
msgstr "`show_goal`（bool）：是否显示目标位置，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1263
msgid ""
"`goal_color` (str): Color of the goal marker. Default is the object's "
"color."
msgstr "`goal_color`（str）：目标标记颜色，默认与对象一致。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1264
msgid "`goal_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the goal marker (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`goal_alpha`（float）：目标透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1265
msgid "`goal_zorder` (int/`1`): Z-order of the goal marker."
msgstr "`goal_zorder`（int）：目标层级，默认 1。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1266
msgid "`show_goal_text` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the goal text."
msgstr "`show_goal_text`（bool）：是否显示目标位置的文本，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1268
msgid "**Text Label Visualization:**"
msgstr "**文本标签可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1269
msgid ""
"`show_text` (bool/`False`): Whether to show text information. By default,"
" the object's abbreviation (e.g., `r0`, `o1`) is displayed. Custom text "
"can be set at runtime via `object.set_text(\"custom label\")`. Pass "
"`None` to reset to the default abbreviation."
msgstr ""
"`show_text`（bool）：是否显示文本信息，默认 False。默认显示对象缩写（如 `r0`、`o1`）。可在运行时通过 "
"`object.set_text(\"自定义文本\")` 设置自定义文本。传入 `None` 可重置为默认缩写。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1270
msgid "`text_color` (str): Color of the text. Default is 'k' (black)."
msgstr "`text_color`（str）：文本颜色，默认 'k'（黑）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1271
msgid "`text_size` (int/`10`): Font size of the text."
msgstr "`text_size`（int）：字体大小，默认 10。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1272
msgid "`text_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the text (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`text_alpha`（float）：文本透明度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1273
msgid "`text_zorder` (int/`2`): Z-order of the text."
msgstr "`text_zorder`（int）：文本层级，默认 2。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1274
msgid ""
"`text_position` (list/`[-radius-0.1, radius+0.1]`): Position offset from "
"object center [dx, dy]."
msgstr "`text_position`（列表）：相对对象中心的偏移 `[dx, dy]`，默认 `[-radius-0.1, radius+0.1]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1276
msgid ""
"Similarly, goal text can be customized via `object.set_goal_text(\"custom"
" goal label\")`."
msgstr "同样，目标文本可通过 `object.set_goal_text(\"自定义目标文本\")` 进行自定义。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1278
msgid "**Velocity Arrow Visualization:**"
msgstr "**速度箭头可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1279
msgid "`show_arrow` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the velocity arrow."
msgstr "`show_arrow`（bool）：是否显示速度箭头，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1280
msgid "`arrow_color` (str/`\"gold\"`): Color of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_color`（str）：箭头颜色，默认 \"gold\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1281
msgid "`arrow_length` (float/`0.4`): Length of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_length`（float）：箭头长度，默认 0.4。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1282
msgid "`arrow_width` (float/`0.6`): Width of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_width`（float）：箭头宽度，默认 0.6。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1283
msgid "`arrow_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the arrow (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`arrow_alpha`（float）：箭头透明度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1284
msgid "`arrow_zorder` (int/`4`): Z-order of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_zorder`（int）：箭头层级，默认 4。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1286
msgid "**Trajectory Path Visualization:**"
msgstr "**轨迹线可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1287
msgid "`show_trajectory` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the trajectory line."
msgstr "`show_trajectory`（bool）：是否显示路径线，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1288
msgid ""
"`traj_color` (str): Color of the trajectory. Default is the object's "
"color."
msgstr "`traj_color`（str）：路径颜色，默认继承对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1289
msgid ""
"`traj_style` (str): Line style of the trajectory (e.g., '-', '--', ':', "
"'-.'). Default is \"-\"."
msgstr "`traj_style`（str）：路径线型（如 '-', '--', ':', '-.'），默认 \"-\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1290
msgid ""
"`traj_width` (float/`None`): Width of the trajectory line. Default is the"
" object's width."
msgstr "`traj_width`（float）：路径线宽，默认为对象宽度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1291
msgid "`traj_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the trajectory (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`traj_alpha`（float）：路径透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1292
msgid "`traj_zorder` (int/`0`): Z-order for trajectory elements."
msgstr "`traj_zorder`（int）：路径层级，默认 0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1293
msgid ""
"`keep_traj_length` (int/`0`): Number of steps to keep from the end of "
"trajectory. Default is 0 (keep all steps)."
msgstr "`keep_traj_length`（int）：保留的尾段步数，默认 0（保留全部）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1295
msgid "**Object Trail Visualization:**"
msgstr "**对象轨迹点可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1296
msgid "`show_trail` (bool/`False`): Whether to show object trails."
msgstr "`show_trail`（bool）：是否显示轨迹点，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1297
msgid "`trail_freq` (int/`2`): Frequency of trail display (every N steps)."
msgstr "`trail_freq`（int）：轨迹显示频率（每 N 步），默认 2。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1298
msgid "`trail_type` (str): Type of trail shape. Default is the object's shape."
msgstr "`trail_type`（str）：轨迹形状类型，默认与对象形状相同。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1299
msgid ""
"`trail_edgecolor` (str): Edge color of the trail. Default is the object's"
" color."
msgstr "`trail_edgecolor`（str）：轨迹边缘颜色，默认为对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1300
msgid "`trail_linewidth` (float/`0.8`): Width of the trail outline."
msgstr "`trail_linewidth`（float）：轨迹线宽，默认 0.8。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1301
msgid "`trail_alpha` (float/`0.7`): Transparency of the trail (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`trail_alpha`（float）：轨迹透明度，默认 0.7。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1302
msgid "`trail_fill` (bool/`False`): Whether to fill the trail shape."
msgstr "`trail_fill`（bool）：是否填充轨迹形状，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1303
msgid ""
"`trail_color` (str): Fill color of the trail. Default is the object's "
"color."
msgstr "`trail_color`（str）：轨迹填充色，默认为对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1304
msgid "`trail_zorder` (int/`0`): Z-order for trail elements."
msgstr "`trail_zorder`（int）：轨迹层级，默认 0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1305
msgid ""
"`keep_trail_length` (int/`0`): Number of steps to keep from the end of "
"trail. Default is 0 (keep all steps)."
msgstr "`keep_trail_length`（int）：保留的轨迹尾段步数，默认 0（保留全部）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1307
msgid "**Sensor Visualization:**"
msgstr "**传感器可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1308
msgid "`show_sensor` (bool/`True`): Whether to show sensor visualizations."
msgstr "`show_sensor`（bool）：是否显示传感器，默认 True。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1310
msgid "**Field of View Visualization:**"
msgstr "**视场可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1311
msgid "`show_fov` (bool/`False`): Whether to show field of view visualization."
msgstr "`show_fov`（bool）：是否显示视场，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1312
msgid "`fov_color` (str/`\"lightblue\"`): Fill color of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_color`（str）：视场填充色，默认 \"lightblue\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1313
msgid "`fov_edge_color` (str/`\"blue\"`): Edge color of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_edge_color`（str）：视场边缘色，默认 \"blue\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1314
msgid "`fov_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the field of view (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`fov_alpha`（float）：视场透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1315
msgid "`fov_zorder` (int/`1`): Z-order of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_zorder`（int）：视场层级，默认 1。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1317
msgid ""
"**Note:** All visual elements are created at the origin during "
"initialization and positioned using matplotlib transforms (for patches) "
"and set_data methods (for lines) during animation updates."
msgstr "**注意：** 所有可视化元素在初始化时创建于原点，并在动画期间通过 matplotlib 的变换（patch）与 set_data（线）定位。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1381
msgid "GUI Configuration"
msgstr "GUI 配置"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1384
msgid "GUI Parameters Table"
msgstr "GUI 参数表"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid "`keyboard`"
msgstr "`keyboard`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid "Keyboard control options (effective when `world.control_mode: keyboard`)."
msgstr "键盘控制选项（当 `world.control_mode: keyboard` 时生效）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid "`mouse`"
msgstr "`mouse`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid "Mouse control options."
msgstr "鼠标控制选项。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**keyboard properties**"
msgstr "**键盘控制**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1395
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**`keyboard`** (`dict`, default: `{}`) Configure keyboard control. "
"Options are read by `KeyboardControl`. The default backend is `pynput`. "
"If `pynput` is unavailable, IR‑SIM automatically falls back to the "
"Matplotlib backend."
msgstr ""
"**`keyboard`**（`dict`，默认值：`{}`）配置键盘控制。选项由 `KeyboardControl` 读取。默认后端为 "
"`pynput`。若 `pynput` 不可用，IR‑SIM 会自动回退到 Matplotlib 后端。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1398
msgid "`backend` (`str`/`\"pynput\"`): Keyboard backend."
msgstr "`backend`（`str`）：键盘后端。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1399
msgid ""
"`\"pynput\"`: Global keyboard hook, but works when the Matplotlib window "
"is focused (requires the `pynput` package)."
msgstr "`\"pynput\"`（默认）：全局键盘hook，但需 Matplotlib 窗口聚焦（依赖 `pynput` 包）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1400
msgid ""
"`\"mpl\"`: Matplotlib figure key events works when the figure window is "
"focused. (no extra dependency, but may be delayed when there are lots of "
"objects)."
msgstr "`\"mpl\"`：Matplotlib 图窗按键事件，仅在窗口聚焦时生效；无额外依赖，但对象数量多时可能有延迟。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1401
msgid ""
"`global_hook` (`bool`/`False`): With `backend: 'pynput'`, capture keys "
"even if the Matplotlib window is not focused. (only active when the "
"window is focused)."
msgstr ""
"`global_hook`（`bool`/`False`）：当 `backend: 'pynput'` 时，即使 Matplotlib "
"窗口未获得焦点也捕获按键。（仅在窗口获得焦点时生效）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1402
msgid "`key_lv_max` (`float`/`3.0`): Maximum linear velocity."
msgstr "`key_lv_max`（`float`）：最大线速度，默认 3.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1403
msgid "`key_ang_max` (`float`/`1.0`): Maximum angular velocity."
msgstr "`key_ang_max`（`float`）：最大角速度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1404
msgid "`key_lv` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial linear velocity."
msgstr "`key_lv`（`float`）：初始线速度，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1405
msgid "`key_ang` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial angular velocity."
msgstr "`key_ang`（`float`）：初始角速度，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1406
msgid ""
"`key_rot` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial rotational velocity (yaw rate for "
"`omni_angular` kinematics)."
msgstr "`key_rot`（`float`）：初始旋转速度（`omni_angular` 运动学下的偏航角速度），默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1407
msgid "`key_id` (`int`/`0`): Initial robot control id."
msgstr "`key_id`（`int`）：初始机器人控制 ID，默认 `0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1423
msgid "**Keyboard Control Keys:**"
msgstr "**键盘控制按键：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1425
msgid "`w` — Forward"
msgstr "`w` — 前进"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1426
msgid "`s` — Backward"
msgstr "`s` — 后退"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1427
msgid "`a` — Turn left (`diff`/`acker`) or strafe left (`omni`/`omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`a` — 左转（`diff`/`acker`）或左侧平移（`omni`/`omni_angular`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1428
msgid "`d` — Turn right (`diff`/`acker`) or strafe right (`omni`/`omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`d` — 右转（`diff`/`acker`）或右侧平移（`omni`/`omni_angular`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1429
msgid "`q` — Rotate left (yaw rate for `omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`q` — 左旋转（`omni_angular` 的偏航角速度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1430
msgid "`e` — Rotate right (yaw rate for `omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`e` — 右旋转（`omni_angular` 的偏航角速度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1431
msgid "`z` / `c` — Decrease / increase maximum angular velocity (`key_ang_max`)"
msgstr "`z` / `c` — 降低 / 提高最大角速度（`key_ang_max`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1432
msgid ""
"`shift+z` / `shift+c` — Decrease / increase maximum linear velocity "
"(`key_lv_max`)"
msgstr "`shift+z` / `shift+c` — 降低 / 提高最大线速度（`key_lv_max`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1433
msgid "`alt+num` — Change Current Control Robot ID"
msgstr "`alt+num` — 更改当前控制的机器人ID"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1434
msgid "`r` — Reset the Environment"
msgstr "`r` — 重置环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1435
msgid "`space` — Toggle Pause/Resume Environment"
msgstr "`space` — 切换暂停/恢复环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1436
msgid "`esc` — Quit the Environment (sets quit flag)"
msgstr "`esc` — 退出环境（设置退出标志）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1437
msgid "`x` — Switch Keyboard/Auto Control"
msgstr "`x` — 切换键盘/自动控制"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1438
msgid "`l` — Reload the Environment"
msgstr "`l` — 重新加载环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1439
msgid "`F5` — Debug the Environment (fn+f5 for mac)"
msgstr "`F5` — 调试环境（Mac上使用fn+f5）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1440
msgid "`v` — Save the current figure"
msgstr "`v` — 保存当前图像"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1441
msgid "`y` — Toggle display render window"
msgstr "`y` — 切换显示渲染窗口"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1444
msgid "Debug mode lets you step the simulation frame-by-frame for inspection:"
msgstr "调试模式可逐帧推进仿真以便检查："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1446
msgid ""
"Press `F5` to enter debug mode at the current frame. While in debug mode,"
" pressing `F5` again advances by one frame (single-step)."
msgstr "按 `F5` 在当前帧进入调试模式，再次按下 `F5` 进入单步。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1447
msgid "Press `space` to exit debug mode and resume normal execution."
msgstr "按 `space` 退出调试模式并恢复正常执行。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1449
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "注意："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1450
msgid ""
"On macOS laptops, you may need to hold the `fn` key (e.g., `fn+F5`). "
"`alt` key is corresponding to `option` key in macOS."
msgstr "在 macOS 笔记本上可能需要配合 `fn` 键（如 `fn+F5`）。`alt` 键对应 `option`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "**mouse properties**"
msgstr "**鼠标控制**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1459
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**`mouse`** (`dict`, default: `{}`) :: Configure mouse control. Options "
"are read by `MouseControl`."
msgstr "**`mouse`**（`dict`，默认 `{}`）：配置鼠标控制，由 `MouseControl` 读取。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1462
msgid "`zoom_factor` (`float`): Zoom factor. Default is `1.1`."
msgstr "`zoom_factor`（`float`）：缩放因子，默认 `1.1`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1472
msgid "**Mouse Actions:**"
msgstr "**鼠标操作：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1474
msgid "**Mouse Movement** — Track mouse position and update display coordinates"
msgstr "**鼠标移动** — 跟踪鼠标位置并更新显示坐标"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1475
msgid "**Middle Click** — Reset zoom to default view"
msgstr "**中键点击** — 重置缩放到默认视图"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1476
msgid "**Scroll Up** — Zoom in (centered on mouse position)"
msgstr "**滚轮向上** — 放大（以鼠标位置为中心）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1477
msgid "**Scroll Down** — Zoom out (centered on mouse position)"
msgstr "**滚轮向下** — 缩小（以鼠标位置为中心）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1479
msgid "**Mouse Position Attributes:**"
msgstr "**鼠标位置属性：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1480
msgid "`left_click_pos` (`tuple`): Position of left click (x, y)."
msgstr "`left_click_pos`（`tuple`）：左键点击位置 (x, y)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1481
msgid "`right_click_pos` (`tuple`): Position of right click (x, y)."
msgstr "`right_click_pos`（`tuple`）：右键点击位置 (x, y)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1482
msgid "`mouse_pos` (`tuple`): Current mouse position (x, y)."
msgstr "`mouse_pos`（`tuple`）：当前鼠标位置 (x, y)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1488
msgid "Configuration Examples"
msgstr "配置示例"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1490
msgid ""
"Let's explore various configuration examples to demonstrate the "
"flexibility and power of IR-SIM:"
msgstr "下面通过多个配置示例展示 IR-SIM 的灵活性与能力："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Multi-Robot RVO"
msgstr "多机器人 RVO"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Multi-Robot ORCA"
msgstr "多机器人ORCA"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Mixed Obstacles"
msgstr "混合障碍"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Ackermann Vehicle"
msgstr "阿克曼车辆"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Omni Angular Robot"
msgstr "全向角速度机器人"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md
msgid "Sensor Integration"
msgstr "传感器集成"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1620
msgid "**Configuration Best Practices:**"
msgstr "**配置最佳实践：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1622
msgid ""
"**Multiple Objects**: When configuring multiple objects, use the `number`"
" and `distribution` parameters to efficiently generate them. For "
"instance, setting `number: 10` with a `distribution` of `'random'` can "
"quickly populate the simulation with randomly placed objects."
msgstr ""
"**多个对象**：配置多个对象时，使用 `number` 和 `distribution` 参数可高效地生成它们。例如，设置 `number: "
"10` 并使用 `'random'` 的 `distribution`，可快速在仿真中随机放置大量对象。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1623
msgid ""
"**Dictionary Parameters**: All dictionary-type parameters (e.g., "
"`distribution`, `shape`, `kinematics`, `behavior`) must include a "
"`'name'` key to specify their type. Omitting the `'name'` key will result"
" in default values or errors."
msgstr ""
"**字典参数**：所有字典类型的参数（如 `distribution`、`shape`、`kinematics`、`behavior`）都必须包含"
" `'name'` 键以指定其类型。省略 `'name'` 键会导致使用默认值或报错。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1624
msgid ""
"**Group Configurations**: By default, objects within the same group share"
" configurations. To customize individual objects within a group, add sub-"
"parameters using `-`. Unspecified objects will inherit the last defined "
"configuration within the group."
msgstr "**分组配置**：同组对象默认共享配置。若需定制，请使用 `-` 添加子参数；未显式配置的对象会继承组内最后一个配置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1625
msgid ""
"**Kinematics and Velocities**: Ensure that the `velocity` and `vel_max` "
"parameters match the kinematics model. For example, a differential drive "
"robot (`'diff'`) uses `[v, omega]`, an omnidirectional robot (`'omni'`) "
"uses body-frame `[forward, lateral]`, and `'omni_angular'` uses "
"`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`."
msgstr ""
"**运动学与速度**：确保 `velocity` 与 `vel_max` 的格式与运动学模型匹配，例如差速 (`'diff'`) 使用 `[v, "
"omega]`，全向 (`'omni'`) 使用机体坐标系 `[forward, lateral]`，`'omni_angular'` 使用 "
"`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1626
msgid ""
"**Plotting Options**: Customize the visualization of your simulation "
"through the `plot` parameter for each object if the `plot` section is "
"located in the object configuration. If it is located in the root of the "
"object configuration, it will be applied to all objects."
msgstr "**绘图选项**：若 `plot` 位于对象配置内部，可为单个对象定制可视化；若位于对象配置的根级，则应用于所有对象。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The configuration file is a YAML "
#~ "file to initialize the environment. It"
#~ " contains the configuration parameters to"
#~ " simulate and visualize the world, "
#~ "obstacle, and robot. You can customize"
#~ " the scenario and define the behavior"
#~ " of the objects simply by using "
#~ "the parameters.配置文件是一个用于初始化环境的 YAML "
#~ "文件。它包含用于模拟和可视化世界、障碍物和机器人的配置参数。使用者可以通过使用这些参数简单地自定义场景并定义对象的行为。"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Parameters such as distribution, shape, "
#~ "behavior, group_behavior, and kinematics must"
#~ " be formatted as `{key: value}` "
#~ "pairs. Ensure that each dictionary "
#~ "includes the `name` key; omitting name"
#~ " will result in a None value "
#~ "for that parameter.诸如分布、形状、行为和运动学等参数必须格式化为 `{key:"
#~ " value}` 对。请确保每个字典都包含 `name` 键；省略 name "
#~ "将导致该参数的值为 None。"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "By default, all objects within the "
#~ "same group share identical configurations. "
#~ "To customize individual objects within a"
#~ " group, add sub-parameters using `-`."
#~ " Any additional objects not explicitly "
#~ "configured will inherit the settings of"
#~ " the last specified object in the "
#~ "group.默认情况下，同一组内的所有对象共享相同的配置。要自定义组内的单个对象，请使用 `-` "
#~ "添加子参数。任何未显式配置的额外对象将继承组中最后一个指定对象的设置。"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Object-level `name` is optional and "
#~ "identifies each object. If omitted, it"
#~ " defaults to `\"<role>_<id>\"` (e.g., "
#~ "`robot_0`, `obstacle_3`). Names must be "
#~ "unique across all objects; duplicates "
#~ "raise an error during environment "
#~ "initialization. Do not confuse object-"
#~ "level `name` with the `name` keys "
#~ "used inside dictionaries like `shape`, "
#~ "`kinematics`, or `behavior` (which indicate"
#~ " component types).对象级别的 `name` "
#~ "是可选的，用于标识每个对象。如果省略，默认为 `\"<role>_<id>\"`（例如 "
#~ "`robot_0`，`obstacle_3`）。名称在所有对象中必须是唯一的；重复的名称会在环境初始化期间引发错误。不要将对象级别的 "
#~ "`name` 与 `shape`、`kinematics` 或 `behavior` "
#~ "等字典中使用的 `name` 键（表示组件类型）混淆。"
#~ msgstr ""

