#~ msgid ""
#~ "`'orca'`: Optimal Reciprocal Collision "
#~ "Avoidance (ORCA) for multi-agent "
#~ "navigation. Requires `pyrvo` package (`pip "
#~ "install pyrvo`). The simulation will "
#~ "attempt to import it only when "
#~ "this behavior is "
#~ "used.`'orca'`：最优互惠碰撞避让（ORCA），用于多智能体导航。需要 `pyrvo` 包（`pip"
